In the Red Bull team today, 180 young, highly qualified professionals equipped with powerful information technology analyze and design every type of modification of racing vehicles.
Siemens explained that the PLM software is capable of analyzing and improving all elements of Red Bull racing vehicles except the engine, for which Renault is fully responsible.
Materials, fuel, aerodynamics and safety features are being modified.
Changes can be converted from virtual reality to reality in less than 24 hours thanks to advanced laser production systems and high-tech autoclaves.
